descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3]
This mod retextures and recolors water. It only changes sea textures, not waterfalls or anything similar.

Parallax will work if you are using ENB, however it isn't strong as RW2.

Installation menu lets you choose between 3 different qualities.

[/size][color=#efefef][size=3]''[/size][/color][color=#ff0000][size=5]Incompatibility[/size][/color][color=#efefef][size=3]''[/size]
[font=Tahoma][size=3]If you are using RW2, put this mod's .esp on top of RW2's .esp. By doing that my .esp will work and RW2's wont.[/size][/font]
[/color][/center]
author: ProtologolusX
